1
00:00:16,080 --> 00:00:17,479
[Previously]
Such a massive operation in a foreign land...

2
00:00:17,560 --> 00:00:19,079
this item must be of utmost importance.

3
00:00:20,520 --> 00:00:21,879
You have no escape.

4
00:00:22,520 --> 00:00:24,599
Watch as I kill every single one of you.

5
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:27,759
So the Elixir of Immortality wants to snatch the treasure too.

6
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:29,399
We've stumbled into a Burial Earth tributary.

7
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:30,760
I am Sanzang.

8
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:31,759
I am Huang.

9
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:32,920
I was just admiring the treasures.

10
00:00:33,400 --> 00:00:35,279
I thought you were from a foreign domain.

11
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:39,919
The Golden Burial Soldiers have marked you.

12
00:00:40,920 --> 00:00:41,999
Your life is almost gone...

13
00:00:42,320 --> 00:00:43,679
and you still have the mood to shop?

14
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:45,799
Since we're here, why panic?

15
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:48,559
Strolling openly and confidently...

16
00:00:48,720 --> 00:00:50,959
is safer than skulking around like a rat.

17
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:54,559
What did you think of that stone and the Withered Blood?

18
00:00:57,120 --> 00:00:58,759
Those are Burial Earth treasures.

19
00:00:58,760 --> 00:01:00,039
Can you even afford them?

20
00:01:00,160 --> 00:01:02,719
You mean the leaf from the Elixir of Immortality?

21
00:01:02,760 --> 00:01:03,279
Do they want it?

22
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:05,359
I advise you to be a decent human being.

23
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:06,759
I'll fight you!

24
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:09,079
Don't think you're the only one with immortal medicine leaves.

25
00:01:09,360 --> 00:01:10,679
So familiar...

26
00:01:15,320 --> 00:01:16,079
Wait.

27
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:18,399
You brat, showing off with *my* leaf?

28
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:23,119
Immortal Medicine is so rare...

29
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:26,079
even the two of us combined only brought one plant.

30
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:29,359
Brother Huang's strength is truly extraordinary.

31
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:37,239
It seems Brother Huang's purpose...

32
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:39,439
is also to enter the Burial Abyss for treasure.

33
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:41,759
The Golden Burial Soldiers all know...

34
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:44,519
that the Immortal Moon Wheels we nurtured...

35
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:47,759
can withstand the Death Light of the Abyss depths.

36
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:50,279
To retrieve celestial treasures and burial relics from within.

37
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:52,519
If you don't understand, speak less to avoid mistakes.

38
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:53,760
Naturally.

39
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:55,199
Listening to him...

40
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:56,839
the Burial Abyss is a land of treasures.

41
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:58,279
Ask fewer questions.

42
00:01:58,440 --> 00:02:01,119
The medicine in that woman's hand probably belongs...

43
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:03,559
to the one deep in the Ancient Burial Domain who raises chickens.

44
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:05,279
She has quite the backing.

45
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,679
What's scary about raising chickens?

46
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,399
He keeps True Phoenixes as chickens...

47
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,079
free-range at that, by the giant wall.

48
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,959
If they aren't his descendants...

49
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:14,959
they must have a Burial King backing them.

50
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,719
They are not to be trifled with.

51
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:17,879
Kid...

52
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,359
they are still watching you.

53
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:21,919
Sooner or later, they'll realize you have no Burial Artifacts to trade.

54
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:24,559
By then, our identities will likely be exposed too.

55
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:25,719
I'm leaving first.

56
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:40,919
Can this item be exchanged?

57
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:43,399
Such precious Burial Earth...

58
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,839
only a Burial King could obtain it.

59
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,519
Brother Huang truly has a noble status.

60
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,759
You spendthrift!

61
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:00,999
You had Myriad Soil and didn't tell me?

62
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,879
I'd strip every leaf off to trade for it!

63
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:06,279
What treasure has Brother Huang found now?

64
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:08,159
Once we enter the depths of the Burial Abyss...

65
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,719
if we truly find the Origin Item...

66
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:11,359
that allows one to become a Burial King...

67
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,559
I hope you'll show your little sister some mercy.

68
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,279
Within the Burial Abyss...

69
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,399
lies the power to achieve the status of a Burial King.

70
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,280
Hahaha!

71
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,239
The Burial Abyss opens!

72
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,159
Brother Huang...

73
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,399
it is time to depart.

74
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,839
The Grand Elder sighed that our world's Dao is flawed...

75
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,799
unable to take the final step.

76
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:38,239
If we can find this item...

77
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:40,039
will it help the Grand Elder?

78
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:49,760
Don't go.

79
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:52,759
The Origin Item is taboo even among Burial Kings.

80
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:54,999
If you value your life, flee!

81
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:57,959
Don't drag me down with you!

82
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,879
Once the Abyss opens...

83
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,879
rare burial treasures will surge forth.

84
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:11,879
Everyone, take them by skill.

85
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,439
As for the deep secrets and treasures...

86
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,239
we may only enter once the Abyss is fully open.

87
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:17,919
These auroras are an omen...

88
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:21,039
that burial treasures are about to emerge.

89
00:04:21,520 --> 00:04:23,079
If Brother Huang doesn't want to fall behind...

90
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,599
now is the time to strike.

91
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,079
It is your turn to act.

92
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:30,559
Now is not the time for me to strike.

93
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,279
That Nine-Eyed Burial Stone of yours...

94
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:34,279
will naturally attract Burial Weapons to worship it.

95
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:40,759
So the stone he selected earlier was the Nine-Eyed Burial Stone.

96
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:42,879
Its value surpasses even Myriad Soil.

97
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,679
I actually missed that...

98
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:53,359
So ferocious, this burial treasure.

99
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:54,479
Even though it only comes to worship...

100
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,439
with no intent to attack...

101
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:56,599
merely its presence...

102
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:58,599
is enough to sever ordinary Burial Soldiers.

103
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,519
Don't you have a body protection technique?

104
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,439
Haven't you heard that different fields have different specializations?

105
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:05,559
My protection method isn't designed against burial weapon aura.

106
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:06,640
It won't hold.

107
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:10,719
Bad news.

108
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,399
Too many Burial Weapons have been attracted.

109
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:14,879
We'll be chopped into scallions by the burial qi.

110
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,439
Quick, take out that Withered Blood!

111
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:17,440
Force them back!

112
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:35,199
We're safe now.

113
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,119
Is it possible the burial artifact is gone too?

114
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,279
Hiss...

115
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:40,159
This isn't my fault, you know.

116
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:41,560
Brother Huang...

117
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,199
this way, I fear none of us will gain anything.

118
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,639
It is not too late to use the treasure after entering the deep palace.

119
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,679
That palace hall, throughout endless ages...

120
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,079
has seen few who could enter.

121
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,120
Too dangerous.

122
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:51,399
Precisely because it is dangerous...

123
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:52,719
true opportunity lies there.

124
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:55,719
Since Brother Huang came to the Burial Abyss for treasure...

125
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,319
you must surely be prepared.

126
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,599
Aside from the Immortal Medicine...

127
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:02,239
why haven't I seen any other burial artifacts for protection?

128
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,479
Why not take them out...

129
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,439
so we may broaden our horizons?

130
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,319
Quick, check.

131
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,519
Which of my weapons can pass for the real thing?

132
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,039
None of these will work.

133
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:12,359
They have no relation to burial artifacts.

134
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,119
Wait...

135
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,119
this one...

136
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:17,719
This is an incredible Ancient Burial Artifact.

137
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,199
Quick!

138
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,279
Take it out fast!

139
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,159
What happened?

140
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:44,079
Brother Huang, you are so boring.

141
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:47,399
I wonder which Burial King's kin...

142
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,479
hides their identity...

143
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,999
making this little sister look like a fool.

144
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,360
This fluctuation...

145
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:55,239
probably buried a True Immortal of the Undying Race.

146
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:56,679
Tell me, Brother Huang...

147
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:58,079
what exactly is your origin?

148
00:06:58,280 --> 00:07:00,159
To be able to pocket such burial treasures.

149
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,159
Just an old trinket.

150
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:03,280
Hardly worth mentioning.

151
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:04,679
Opportunity lies before us.

152
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,719
Priority should be taking the burial treasures.

153
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:10,639
Could the Dark God Son have been a Burial Soldier?

154
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:11,639
Perhaps.

155
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,639
The Underworld is also related to the Burial Earth.

156
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:18,759
This burial soil nurtures the vitality of the Primordial Era.

157
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,239
Not only does it nourish immortal medicine...

158
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:23,119
it also allows us Burial Soldiers to leap in cultivation.

159
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:25,119
Apologies, Brother Huang...

160
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:26,959
but I must get there first!

161
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:27,959
Tsk.

162
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:30,079
This damn competitive spirit.

163
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:30,679
Er Xue...

164
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:31,920
use the Nine-Eyed Stone...

165
00:07:32,080 --> 00:07:34,359
to collect all this burial soil.

166
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:39,079
Then open the cauldron to collect the treasures.

167
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,479
Brother Huang, show mercy...

168
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:49,119
share some with us, will you?

169
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,359
You fool.

170
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:56,679
Such top-tier burial soil, and you give it away so casually?

171
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:57,959
Stick with me...

172
00:07:57,960 --> 00:07:59,479
and forget this silver sand...

173
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:01,639
even my one-zhang cube of Myriad Soil...

174
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:03,359
is yours to take root in.

175
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:04,919
Ah...

176
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,759
Thanks for showing mercy, Brother Huang.

177
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,599
With more burial treasures for protection...

178
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:10,239
once the Burial King restriction lifts...

179
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:12,519
we can also go stir up trouble in the foreign domain.

180
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:14,679
Though the Burial Soldiers didn't collude with the foreign lands...

181
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:15,999
their temperament is eccentric.

182
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:19,559
Once they emerge, I fear they will cause waves of turmoil again.

183
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,919
This aura...

184
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,319
why does it feel so familiar?

185
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,120
The Dark Cage...

186
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:40,079
a living being is escaping from inside.

187
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:56,199
A supreme being has emerged!

188
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,200
Dodge!

189
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,039
It is the legendary...

190
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:03,199
Lord Ru Gu, who was about to become an Immortal!

191
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,719
He has also lost his soul!

192
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:11,119
(Ancient Burial Language)

193
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:12,800
What is he shouting?

194
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,199
His accent is too thick...

195
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,280
how would I know?

196
00:09:15,304 --> 00:09:28,304
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

197
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:37,519
A Burial Soldier of this level...

198
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,799
could crush us to dust with a wave of his hand.

199
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,120
Run!

200
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,199
What is the origin of this chest?

201
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,200
It's so sturdy.

202
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,839
Ask less about what you shouldn't ask.

203
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:48,559
If this chest were so easy to destroy...

204
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:50,359
it would have rotted away in that grave long ago.

205
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,320
Suppress.

206
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:27,959
Looking at the direction that Lord came from...

207
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:30,519
could it be the rumored Lord of Our World...

208
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:32,319
sealed deep within the Burial Abyss?

209
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:39,479
Such overwhelming power just now...

210
00:11:39,680 --> 00:11:42,079
was merely a flick of my Lord's finger.

211
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:43,799
Brother Huang...

212
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:45,239
what kind of burial artifact is this chest?

213
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,599
It is indestructible.

214
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:47,639
Truly extraordinary.

215
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:50,239
I am very interested in the patterns on its surface.

216
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,999
Might I observe them for a moment?

217
00:11:52,040 --> 00:11:53,040
Please.

218
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:00,759
How wondrous.

219
00:12:00,920 --> 00:12:02,999
These patterns bring clarity to the mind...

220
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,039
making one feel on the verge of enlightenment.

221
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,359
Yet the chest itself...

222
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,599
inspires disgust.

223
00:12:06,640 --> 00:12:07,559
Such a contradiction.

224
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:10,919
It seems this chest is indeed related to the Burial Soldiers.

225
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,039
Old Medicine...

226
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,319
what do you know?

227
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:14,840
Ah...

228
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:16,759
between knowing and knowing...

229
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:17,959
there are differences.

230
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:20,239
Some things, once known, can be said.

231
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:22,719
Others, once known, are not necessarily sayable.

232
00:12:23,760 --> 00:12:25,519
And some things are...

233
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,839
things you wouldn't understand even if I told you.

234
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:35,159
I knew the Burial Abyss opening would be unpredictable...

235
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:36,559
finding the Great Dao amidst life and death.

236
00:12:37,160 --> 00:12:38,959
That is the path a warrior should walk.

237
00:12:40,760 --> 00:12:42,079
This martial fanatic...

238
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:44,439
Brother Huang, care to join?

239
00:12:45,520 --> 00:12:47,279
Inside the Abyss lies not only the Burial Five Opportunity...

240
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:50,279
but perhaps also the truth behind this rotten wooden chest.

241
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,240
Let's go.

242
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:03,239
Everyone saw it.

243
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:05,239
The giant hand that shocked the Heavenly Abyss...

244
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:07,479
appeared precisely where Huang had gone.

245
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:09,679
He is most likely colluding with the foreign domain...

246
00:13:09,760 --> 00:13:11,159
to create such an omen.

247
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:13,199
Huang once severed ten Kings...

248
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,919
bearing a blood feud with the foreign lands.

249
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:15,999
No matter who the traitor is...

250
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:17,359
it can never be him.

251
00:13:17,520 --> 00:13:19,519
Whoever splashes dirty water on my brother...

252
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:20,879
calling him a defector to the foreign lands...

253
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:22,559
is clearly a thief crying "stop thief."

254
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:24,599
Who told Huang to return so late?

255
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:27,599
Someone used the Imperial Pass teleportation array to go to the foreign domain.

256
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:29,359
This is ironclad evidence.

257
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:31,799
We will not wrong a good person...

258
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:33,879
nor let a bad person go.

259
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:34,239
G...

260
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:34,599
G...

261
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:36,159
Until the truth is revealed...

262
00:13:36,400 --> 00:13:38,959
no one is to leave the pass.

263
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:41,879
Since it is confirmed that the traitor is not Huang...

264
00:13:42,040 --> 00:13:43,799
we should bring him back immediately.

265
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:46,399
You lot are clearly trying to obstruct the rescue.

266
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:50,359
Huang recklessly charged into the Sacred Medicine Mountain Range...

267
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:52,359
and now you want to waste the elite of Imperial Pass to save him?

268
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,479
Are other people's lives not lives?

269
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:56,159
A bunch of cowards.

270
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:57,919
I will ask my Master to act personally.

271
00:13:58,680 --> 00:13:59,919
I don't believe we can't save Huang.

272
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,479
Ignorant fools.

273
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:04,199
You have no right to speak here.

274
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:09,439
A student of my Heavenly God Academy...

275
00:14:09,520 --> 00:14:11,159
needs no discipline from the Wang family.

276
00:14:12,920 --> 00:14:14,959
Pass my greetings to your Master.

277
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:16,719
However, given the current situation...

278
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:18,839
there is no need to disturb the old man.

279
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,839
I will go alone...

280
00:14:21,040 --> 00:14:22,639
and bring Huang back.

281
00:14:22,800 --> 00:14:23,800
Senior...

282
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:24,920
your severe injuries are not yet healed.

283
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:26,439
It would be best to go to the Ancestral Altar...

284
00:14:26,640 --> 00:14:28,239
and invite one or two Supreme Beings to assist.

285
00:14:29,920 --> 00:14:31,919
Huang is my disciple.

286
00:14:32,040 --> 00:14:33,959
Naturally, I must act personally.

287
00:14:34,760 --> 00:14:37,479
If others from Imperial Pass suffer losses because of this...

288
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:39,079
my heart will not be at peace.

289
00:14:43,880 --> 00:14:45,999
He is burning the Supreme Battle Blood within him.

290
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:48,239
That terrifying power from before...

291
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:49,639
was not even his full strength.

292
00:15:18,160 --> 00:15:19,239
He broke through again.

293
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:22,359
This is the invincible bearing that suppressed an era.

294
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:23,879
And yet...

295
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:25,719
he is still getting stronger.

296
00:16:01,680 --> 00:16:03,679
Senior Meng actually succeeded in reversing aging...

297
00:16:03,840 --> 00:16:05,039
and regained his youth!

298
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:07,599
The Grand Elder was so handsome when he was young...

299
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:08,600
radiating brilliance.

300
00:16:08,960 --> 00:16:10,479
Now that is a true hero.

301
00:16:18,680 --> 00:16:19,680
I hope...

302
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:22,119
I am not too late.

303
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:29,000
[Episode 267 — Power Rankings - 1.Funeral King, 2.Bone Sovereign, 3.Shi Hao (Full Power) 4.Golden Supreme / Tu Mingxuan 5.Wang Yu, 6.Huang]

304
00:16:29,024 --> 00:16:58,424
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

